        "body" : "Unfortunately at the moment `Min` and `Max` always return doubles.\r\n\r\nIdeally we would return the exact column type for calls like `Max<T>(\"x\")` and double for jitted calls, `Max(\"x\")`, but I never had the time to implement the required logic.",
