        "authorId" : "a66b5f61-1206-4ddd-b280-befb0005276f",
        "body" : "Here is an example of why I think this is a bad idea:\r\n```\r\n$ root -l\r\nroot [0] x = 10101010101010101010.0;\r\nroot [1] x\r\n(double) 10101010101010100224.000000\r\nroot [2] \r\n```",
